node.text: It's done! @cambridgecaraudio have completed the install and fine tuning of the the new @audison_official @fourcaraudio Thesis sound system in @theshmeemobiles SLS AMG Black Series. node.text: The new seats are in @theshmeemobiles AMG GT R Roadster and absolutely looking the part! Thanks to @opus_innovation, I've swapped out the original Performance Seats in favour of the OEM buckets you find in the Coupe (and GT BS, GT R Pro, SLS BS etc) which are not only more comfortable, but save around 15kg per seat, and look the part too! Not only that, but they've coded the software to still handle comfort access with the electric steering column, and even installed seat heating that operates on the dash buttons too. I bought the seats nearly a year ago, waiting to do this upgrade, and could not be happier with the result and how it transforms the car for me. Now, it's time for some laps at the @nuerburgring #Mercedes #AMG #AMGGTR #GTRRoadster #Shmeemobile #Opus #Shmee150

node.text: It's time for the new seats in @theshmeemobiles GT R Roadster! These have been with @opus_innovation since I bought them late last year, but finally restrictions and timings allow the installation to be carried out. We have an OEM set of GT R seats (not available for the Roadster) that even have had heating added, but where you might think the installation just takes moments, there's also a software complication. Because it has the electric steering column, that's controlled by the ECU from the seats, and obviously without those it'll be stuck so some coding is required hence why it's in the hands of @opus_innovation who know exactly what to do! #Mercedes #AMG #AMGGTR #GTRRoadster #Opus #Shmee150
